{"id":1284128105,"question_id":8,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"1 year, 1 month","timestamp":1718043752,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"3 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1284128105/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"String to Integer (atoi)","memory":"8.2 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int myAtoi(string s) {\n        int i = 0, n = s.length();\n        \n        // Step 1: Skip leading whitespace\n        while (i < n && s[i] == ' ') ++i;\n        \n        // Step 2: Check sign\n        int sign = 1;\n        if (i < n && (s[i] == '-' || s[i] == '+')) {\n            sign = (s[i] == '-') ? -1 : 1;\n            ++i;\n        }\n        \n        // Step 3: Convert digits\n        long result = 0;\n        while (i < n && isdigit(s[i])) {\n            result = result * 10 + (s[i] - '0');\n            \n            // Step 4: Check for overflow\n            if (result * sign > INT_MAX) return INT_MAX;\n            if (result * sign < INT_MIN) return INT_MIN;\n            \n            ++i;\n        }\n        \n        return result * sign;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"string-to-integer-atoi","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1,"frontend_id":57}
